sequenceDiagram
    actor Admin
    participant Browser
    participant API as API Routes
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Admin->>Browser: Click "Users" in the navigation bar
    Browser->>API: GET /api/users
    API->>DB: User.findMany(select: id, name, email, role, subscription)
    DB-->>API: All users
    API-->>Browser: User list
    Browser-->>Admin: Display user table

    Admin->>Browser: Click Role cell → select new role
    Browser->>API: POST /api/users
    Note right of Browser: { userId, role: "Admin" | "Staff" | blank }
    API->>DB: Validate: session.user.role === ADMIN
    API->>DB: User.update(where: userId, data: { role })
    DB-->>API: Updated user
    API-->>Browser: 200 OK
